<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>TaskQuest - Gamified Task Management</title>
  <link href="/styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-purple-200 min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
  <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-95 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-10 max-w-2xl w-full flex flex-col items-center">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-purple-700 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span>TaskQuest</span>
      <span class="text-2xl">🧙‍♂️⚒️</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 text-center">
      TaskQuest transforms mundane task tracking into a collaborative RPG-style adventure.<br>
      Complete story-driven quests, earn XP, level up, and get real-time WhatsApp notifications!
    </p>
    <div class="w-full mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-3 text-center">🔥 Core Features</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-xl">🎯</span>
          <span><strong>Quest Creation:</strong> Break tasks into quests with descriptions, XP, and clear steps</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-xl">🧱</span>
          <span><strong>Task Chain:</strong> Users complete tasks step-by-step, like RPG objectives</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-xl">📈</span>
          <span><strong>XP & Leveling System:</strong> Earn XP and level up based on quest completion</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-xl">💬</span>
          <span><strong>WhatsApp Integration:</strong> Real-time updates through WhatsApp (Twilio API)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-xl">👤</span>
          <span><strong>User Progress Tracking:</strong> Track current step, completion status, and quest history</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-xl">📚</span>
          <span><strong>GraphQL API:</strong> Clean, scalable backend with Apollo + Express + MongoDB</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <a href="#" class="px-8 py-3 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-lg font-semibold shadow hover:bg-purple-700 transition text-lg mt-2">Start Your Quest</a>
  </div>
  <footer class="mt-10 text-gray-500 text-sm">
    &copy; 2025 TaskQuest. All rights reserved.
  </footer>
</body>
</html> 